\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {8}{\ignorespaces Schedule-driven model (Model 3): estimated importation intensity and $P(\geq 1)$ for all five diseases across all US venue cities, decomposed into WC-fan and background travel streams. WC fan routing follows the match schedule; background routing uses T-100 fractions.}}{36}{figure.caption.76}\protected@file@percent }
