\newlabel{fig:comp_prob}{{9}{37}{Three-model comparison: probability of at least one importation $[P(\geq 1)]$ by venue city and disease. \textcolor {blue}{Blue} = Baseline; \textcolor {red}{Red} = WC-adjusted; \textcolor {green!60!black}{Green} = Schedule-driven. Cities absent from a model show $P = 0$ for that model by construction}{figure.caption.78}{}}
